Izy toilet pistols.

"Black Wolf's AC and Heater inside vehicles (A21 - 1.0 - 2.0)" Vehicles, enabled.
Does what it says.

"Ophidiophobia - True Zombie Survival (No Snakes Wolves Bears Vultures)" Zombies, disabled.
Removes these creatures from global spawning, and replaces some of them with zombies in POIs.

New stuff:

"Craft Clothing for 2.5" Standard, enabled.
From the Author:
Adds recipes to allow players the ability to craft the (thermal insulating) clothing items brought back into 2.5.
Currently in 2.5, you cannot craft or buy them from traders.
Until TFP fixes that issue in a future update, I made this mod so we can at least craft them. 
I gated the ability to craft these items by locking tier 2 and 3 behind workstations:
Craft Tier 1 Clothing within the Backpack.
Craft Tier 2 Clothing within the Workbench.
Craft Tier 3 Clothing within the Chemistry Station. You must search "Clothing" within the Chemistry Station to find it!

